WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.190
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.269
Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:08.230
It's Diana and me. She's

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.790
behind the camera and she's been

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.950
reading to me all day. Our internet's

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:14.709
been down because we had a big storm

00:00:14.719 --> 00:00:16.230
come through last night, but we got a

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.150
lot of rain again and the Lord blessed

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:22.630
us. But with no internet, no videos. So,

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:23.790
we've been

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.230
reading and she read a lot of things

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:27.589
in the Old Testament to me from

00:00:27.599 --> 00:00:29.910
Nehemiah. And I told her, I said, 'You

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:31.269
know, this is really interesting. Some

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:34.069
of these prophetic men that walked the

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:35.590
face of the earth went through so

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.110
much. You know, I have nothing to

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:39.910
complain about when I hear the

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:41.590
stories of what they went through. I

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.869
mean, my goodness! But

00:00:43.879 --> 00:00:47.590
this is the book we

00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:47.600
found.'And

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:49.069
Sister

00:00:49.069 --> 00:00:49.079
Billye

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:52.790
Brim, the big prayer warrior, my

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.470
mama prayer warrior is what I call

00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:54.480
her—she

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:57.069
is an amazing woman of

00:00:57.069 --> 00:00:57.079
God—she

00:00:57.079 --> 00:01:01.830
told us about this book this

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:03.990
week, and I just wanted to tell you

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.990
all this book is

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:10.469
amazing if you find it. It's on Amazon,

00:01:10.479 --> 00:01:12.469
right? Yeah. Or you can find it on eBay

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:14.789
or probably a lot of other sites. Yeah,

00:01:14.799 --> 00:01:16.310
there's probably a lot of places you can

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:17.910
find it. You just have to Google it or

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:20.070
whatever and you can find this book. But

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:22.950
I encourage every believer to read it. I

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:25.830
think you read half of it today, Timmy.

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:29.030
But it gets you so excited

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:31.350
about heaven. It gets you so excited

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:34.870
about what's coming. Folks, the future's

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:37.670
bright. I just told Diana, I

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.830
said, 'I have to take a break. You

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:42.230
have to read it slower because I

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:44.950
want to download and just process

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:47.030
what this man is saying about what he

00:01:47.030 --> 00:01:47.040
saw.'He

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:49.590
had an accident—not to be a spoiler

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:51.830
alert, but he had an

00:01:51.830 --> 00:01:51.840
accident—and

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:54.550
he died for eight hours and he came

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:58.550
back, and the testimony of what the

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.510
Lord showed him when he was there is

00:02:01.520 --> 00:02:04.789
breathtaking. It's just absolutely wow.

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:07.350
So, I encourage you to read this book. I

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:09.430
don't know him, but she recommended

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:12.869
it and I trust her immensely. So, all

00:02:12.879 --> 00:02:15.750
right. But let me tell you now what

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:18.270
I saw the last time we prayed

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:21.430
together. He showed me an alarm clock

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:25.430
with hands straight up. I saw the

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:28.390
alarm clock going off, and there was

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:32.990
a man in the bed

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.070
asleep, and he was not hearing the alarm

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.790
clock that was so loud going off above

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.509
him. It was on a shelf, and I could

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:43.589
see the room was white and it

00:02:43.599 --> 00:02:45.430
had books on the shelf. It was a bedroom

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:47.350
and I could see the person. He was

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.630
asleep and the alarm clock was going

00:02:50.630 --> 00:02:50.640
off,

00:02:50.640 --> 00:02:53.190
but because he did not

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:55.750
wake up, the Lord said, 'Now there's

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:59.430
going to be a great shaking to

00:02:59.430 --> 00:02:59.440
awaken.'And

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:02.710
I saw the Lord taking the body of

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:06.070
this man and moving him like this to

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:09.670
wake him up. And He said, 'What's about

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:14.229
to take place will wake up the remnant.

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:17.270
Most of the people—what's about to take

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:20.110
place will wake up

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:22.070
everyone. I don't know how you're going

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:24.309
to sleep through what's coming, but

00:03:24.319 --> 00:03:28.470
maybe some will, but most will wake

00:03:28.470 --> 00:03:28.480
up.'And

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:29.949
so

00:03:29.959 --> 00:03:33.270
then the Lord said to me, 'You want the

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.589
greater glory. You want the greater

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:37.910
outpouring, and this is what it's going

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:41.070
to take to get it.'And I saw each

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:43.910
person, each individual person, we were

00:03:43.920 --> 00:03:45.990
all different colors. We all

00:03:45.990 --> 00:03:46.000
had

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:50.309
different garments on, but each

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:52.949
one of us was playing an instrument in

00:03:52.959 --> 00:03:56.630
an orchestra. Some were the brass with

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:59.589
the tubas and the horns

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:01.509
and all the trumpets and all the

00:04:01.519 --> 00:04:04.229
beautiful sound. Some of them were the

00:04:04.239 --> 00:04:05.910
drums. Some of them were the

00:04:05.910 --> 00:04:05.920
cymbals.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.149
Some were the chimes, some of them were

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:11.710
the harps—all the beautiful things,

00:04:11.720 --> 00:04:15.589
right? But as we played together as one

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:19.949
body, we made beautiful music

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:23.189
together. And then I saw a puzzle, and

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:25.590
each person was a puzzle piece to what

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.909
God wanted to do to join His bride

00:04:27.919 --> 00:04:30.790
and His people together. But He said to

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:33.189
me, 'So many of My people in the body

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:35.550
have gone and started to be

00:04:35.550 --> 00:04:35.560
lone

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:38.790
rangers. They don't want to be a body

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:40.629
anymore because they're

00:04:40.629 --> 00:04:40.639
offended.'So

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:43.390
they say, 'Well, I serve the

00:04:43.400 --> 00:04:46.790
Lord by myself. I don't have to have a

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.629
relationship with the church because

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:50.390
they've hurt me. I don't want to be a

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:51.909
part of the church.'And they had an

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:53.189
attitude about the church. So they just

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:54.710
said, 'Well, I'm a Christian. I

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.629
fellowship by myself.'And they just

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:59.110
wanted to be alone like a lone ranger.

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:01.749
And He said, 'There are no more lone

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:04.469
rangers in the body of Christ. You must

00:05:04.479 --> 00:05:08.189
come together as the days

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:11.430
approach. Forsake not the assembling

00:05:11.430 --> 00:05:11.440
of

00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:12.590
yourselves

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:14.350
together,

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:17.430
and even more so

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.909
as the days get closer and

00:05:19.909 --> 00:05:19.919
closer.'Basically,

00:05:19.919 --> 00:05:21.670
what the Word says. He said,

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:24.310
'Brandon, I'm calling My body back

00:05:24.310 --> 00:05:24.320
together.'And

00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:25.909
He said,

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:27.749
'If you don't get along with that fold,

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:29.990
then repent and go find one

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.469
that you

00:05:31.479 --> 00:05:34.310
can, and be led by the Spirit of

00:05:34.320 --> 00:05:36.790
the Lord and find a body that you can go

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:39.510
to and be a part of that

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.270
congregation that you feel comfortable

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:43.350
being with. But don't make the

00:05:43.350 --> 00:05:43.360
excuse,

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:45.230
'I'm a lone ranger. I serve the Lord by

00:05:45.230 --> 00:05:45.240
myself.'Okay,

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:47.749
that's what He was saying

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:50.550
to me in this vision.

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:53.350
And He said, 'Each one of My kids is a

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:56.310
vital part of the puzzle. Each one of My

00:05:56.310 --> 00:05:56.320
kids—there's

00:05:56.320 --> 00:05:58.629
not one greater and

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:01.830
there's not one smaller. Each person

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:05.430
provides music and brings their supply.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:10.390
They bring their supply to prayer, their

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:13.430
supply to the church, and each person

00:06:13.440 --> 00:06:16.230
brings that supply, and it makes us all

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:19.830
sound beautiful together.'But if you

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:23.670
hear some drum off by itself, it's

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:26.870
just a drum. But a drum that's with a

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:26.880
choir

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:28.870
with an orchestra sounds

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:30.390
beautiful, doesn't it? It makes beautiful

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:32.749
music. You go,

00:06:32.749 --> 00:06:32.759
'Wow.'It's

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:35.350
so important that we

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.950
function as a body, is what the Lord

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:40.150
said. Without strife, without discord,

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:42.670
without all this stuff, we flow

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.790
together. And it was beautiful, the way

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:46.469
He painted the whole picture to me. I

00:06:46.479 --> 00:06:48.150
was like, 'Wow.'And then He talked

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:51.510
about Acts chapter 2, verse 1, I

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:53.830
believe it is—I don't remember exactly,

00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:56.070
it was around there. He talked about

00:06:56.080 --> 00:06:59.749
how, before the great

00:06:59.759 --> 00:07:02.550
mighty wind of the Holy Spirit with

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.950
cloven tongues as of fire, they were all

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:07.550
joined together in one

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:10.710
accord, with one voice, with one accord.

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:14.070
And then a sound from heaven as a mighty

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:18.070
rushing wind came. But before the great

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:20.870
outpouring of the Holy

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:23.430
Spirit in Acts chapter 2, they were of

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:25.309
one voice and one

00:07:25.319 --> 00:07:27.670
accord. And the Lord said, 'This is what

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:30.990
I'm looking for. If you want the greater

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:33.749
outpouring, you must be one voice and

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:37.950
one accord in prayer, functioning as a

00:07:37.960 --> 00:07:43.189
body. Not lone rangers, as a

00:07:43.189 --> 00:07:43.199
body—one

00:07:43.199 --> 00:07:46.670
voice, one sound flowing

00:07:46.670 --> 00:07:46.680
together.'And

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:49.670
then He talked to me about

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:52.270
that. He said, 'I'm bringing the

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:55.270
finances because I saw a rocket

00:07:55.270 --> 00:07:55.280
ship.'And

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:56.710
He said, 'I'm taking you to the

00:07:56.720 --> 00:07:58.950
outer stratosphere.'He used a word that

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:01.270
I'm not really familiar with. And He

00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:03.110
told me, He said, 'Brandon, I'm taking

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:06.309
this rocket ship, but the rocket fuel is

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:09.029
going to be the finances.'And He said

00:08:09.039 --> 00:08:11.350
it will be so much so that He gave me

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:15.029
the scripture of Moses and how he told

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:17.270
the children of Israel, 'There's too

00:08:17.280 --> 00:08:19.430
much. You can't bring any more of all

00:08:19.440 --> 00:08:21.430
the blessing because we don't have

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:24.629
enough room to receive it all.'And the

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:26.790
Lord said to me, 'There will be such a

00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:29.790
surplus and such a blessing on My

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:33.190
body, to the remnant of the people who

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:35.269
will listen to me on what to do with

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:37.350
their finances, that it'll be such

00:08:37.350 --> 00:08:37.360
a

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:39.110
surplus that you'll have more than

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.750
enough to pay for the churches, for the

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:44.550
food, for water, for whatever you've got

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:46.550
to do to bring in this end-time harvest

00:08:46.560 --> 00:08:48.790
because the people are coming in.'And

00:08:48.790 --> 00:08:48.800
there

00:08:48.800 --> 00:08:51.110
won't be a lack among anybody.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:53.509
Remember when it said in

00:08:53.509 --> 00:08:53.519
Acts—also

00:08:53.519 --> 00:08:56.710
it said that they sold all

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:59.670
their possessions and they brought all

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:01.750
the money in, and nobody lacked any good

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.389
thing? Nobody lacked anything. There was

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:05.990
abundance for everybody because

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:09.150
everybody took care of

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:11.910
everybody. They were a family. That's

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:13.590
why every time I start these

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:16.550
videos, I say, 'Good morning,

00:09:16.550 --> 00:09:16.560
family.'Because

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.110
when we get on the other side

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:21.269
and you read this book, you're going to

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:24.710
see that we're a family up there. We're

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:26.870
the family of God. We're the family. We

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:29.829
are a family. We're not like, 'Oh, well,

00:09:29.839 --> 00:09:31.590
you know.'He even talks

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:32.269
about

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:34.870
how there are no locks on any doors

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:34.880
because

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:36.389
there's no crime, but everybody just

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:39.269
visits everybody and talks to everybody.

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:40.949
You go and visit your friend from down

00:09:40.959 --> 00:09:42.230
the road, and you're saying, "Hey, how

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.710
are you doing?"at their mansion. You

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.870
go down the road and you see there

00:09:46.870 --> 00:09:46.880
are

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:49.030
kids outside playing in

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:51.910
heaven. He said it's a

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:55.110
glorious family, learning and

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:59.630
fellowshipping, and folks, it's

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.910
wonderful. But it's not about everybody

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:04.470
being in strife; it's about walking in

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:06.870
love. And I understand there's a lot of

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:08.550
people with a lot of different beliefs

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:10.150
because there is a lot of

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:13.110
different thinking and because we've

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:15.269
all been raised differently. I get it. But

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.350
God wants us to come together and

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:19.990
be one-minded, of one faith in the days

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:22.750
ahead. And there'll be one great

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:24.870
revival. There's going to be one great

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:27.190
revival. And so that's what I had for

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:29.590
you today. That's basically a rundown

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:31.750
of the prayer time we had last time. And

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:34.550
it was beautiful to me because I saw the

00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:37.030
Father's heart concerning each one of us,

00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:39.110
that there's not one greater and there's

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:41.910
not one smaller or better or whatever.

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:43.990
It's just we're all a part of the puzzle,

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:47.269
and we are a vital piece. You're a vital

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:50.069
piece to God's plan.

00:10:50.079 --> 00:10:52.550
Every single one of

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:55.269
you is a vital piece to God's plan for

00:10:55.279 --> 00:10:57.750
the future, what He wants to do on

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:59.509
this earth, and what He wants to do in

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:03.110
heaven for the thousand-year reign.

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.710
Every single one of us has a vital

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:08.310
part. Let's pray for Elon today.

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:12.069
Okay, after I've said all that, it's

00:11:12.079 --> 00:11:14.389
on my heart to pray for him. I know I've

00:11:14.399 --> 00:11:18.150
made some of you mad, and you

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:21.190
are on his bandwagon. You love

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:23.030
him, and you think you know him and all

