believe that he's a rat and all these

00:11:35.120 --> 00:11:36.949
things, that's fine, folks. I get it.

00:11:36.959 --> 00:11:38.710
I'm just here to relay it, but I'm not

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:41.190
here to make enemies. But let's pray.

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:43.670
Let's pray for him today. You know,

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:45.269
